Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.game_components

Enum Class Character

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Character>
it.polimi.ingsw.model.game_components.Character
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Character>, Constable
public enum Character extends Enum<Character>
Class that enumerates all the Characters of the game and contains the methods to get information about them and to update their status.
